ildren", "Facebook", "Twitter", "LinkedIn", "GooglePlus", "Students with children", "Trying to study while raising a family? Feeling isolated? Connect with the", "Concordia University Student Parents Centre (CUSP)", "! We provide an accessible space to study but also a place to share interests and develop a support network. Drop by the Centre to see how we can help you achieve your academic goals.", "Our space", "We're a child-friendly space on campus. Come visit! We have a computer lab, a kitchen and a lounge for you to use.", "Check out our space", "Our space", "We're a child-friendly space on campus. Come visit! We have a computer lab, a kitchen and a lounge for you to use.", "Programs & events", "CUSP support student parents many ways: a computer lab and lounge, a school supplies program, winter coat and toy bazaars and more.", "Go to programs & events", "Programs & events", "CUSP support student parents many ways: a computer lab and lounge, a school supplies program, winter coat and toy bazaars and more.", "Finances & budgeting", "Here are a list of provincial and Concordia resources to help support your family while you study.", "Sort out your finances", "Finances & budgeting", "Here are a list of provincial and Concordia resources to help support your family while you study.", "How to find childcare", "While CUSP does not provide childcare, we keep up-to-date information on childcare and contacts for", "Concordia's two CPE daycares", ".", "Find childcare", "How to find childcare", "While CUSP does not provide childcare, we keep up-to-date information on childcare and contacts for", "Concordia's two CPE daycares", ".", "Sign up with CUSP", "Become a member", "Volunteer with us", "Events", "More events", "Upcoming", "Dec. 17", "Les Petits Profs Family Cineclub - FROZEN film screening", "10 a.m. \u2014 11:45 a.m.", "Past", "Dec. 18", "Student Parents Bakeout", "2 p.m. \u2014 5 p.m.", "Past", "Dec. 10", "CUSP Holiday Party 2016", "2 p.m. \u2014 5 p.m.", "Photo gallery", "Announcements", "Volunteer at CUSP", "We are looking for volunteers that love working with children and are interested in helping them with their English, French or Math homework.", "Learn more", "Free goods bazaar: drop-off dates", "Cleaning out your closets, get rid of slightly used clothing or toys and books for children and adults? We're holding our annual Free Goods Bazaar to help students that are studying while raising a family.", "See event", "Affordable food", "In collaboration with both our Professionals in Student Services Departments and external Professionals, CUSP offers a wide range of workshops tailored to your specific needs as student parents.\u00a0 The workshops cover topics such as managing your finances, creating and maintaining balance in your life, all to help you succeed in your academic career.", "Find affordable food", "Concordia University Student Parents Centre", "Contact us", "(514) 848-2424, ext. 2431", "cusp@concordia.ca", "Locations & hours", "Sir George Williams Campus", "TD-24 (see map)", "1410 Guy St. - Room 24", "2nd floor (via the elevator)", "Monday - Friday", "10 a.m. to 6 p.m.", "Connect with us", "Join us on Facebook", "Back to top", "\u00a9 Concordia University", "Concordia University", "- Call us at 514-848-2424", "About", "Academics", "Admissions", "Campus life", "Research", "International", "Future students", "Current students", "Alumni & friends", "Parents", "Faculty & staff", "Media", "Sir George Williams Campus", "1455 De Maisonneuve Blvd. W.", "Montreal", ",", "Quebec", ",", "Canada", "H3G 1M8", "See SGW Campus map", "Loyola Campus", "7141 Sherbrooke Street W.", "Montreal", ",", "Quebec", ",", "Canada", "H4B 1R6", "See Loyola Campus map", "facebook", "twitter", "google", "youtube", "linkedin", "pinterest", "instagram", "flickr", "Concordia social", "\u00a9 Concordia University", "Terms", "Privacy", "Accessibility", "Website feedback", "Share this page", "Concordia.ca", "Call us at", "514-848-2424", "Sir Georg